node.content: ["One person is in a moderate condition after a paraglider incident near W\u0101naka.", "St John says it received a call to the Treble Cone Skifield area at 12:06pm on Tuesday, and an ambulance and helicopter responded.", "The helicopter is currently on the scene.", "Police say they're also responding to the incident.", "St John anticipates they will have more information to give later on."]
